comments: VanVleet (TOR) is established in Butler's (MIA) path and marginal body contact occurs prior to VanVleet cleanly dislodging Butler of the ball.
Barnes (TOR) engages and disengages with Butler (MIA) as the defensive switch takes place.

Replay review of the foul called on Siakam (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Siakam extends his left leg and initiates contact with Adebayo's (MIA) lower half as he starts his drive. However, the contact was deemed to have occurred prior to Adebayo's gather and the play was overturned to a non-shooting foul.
VanVleet (TOR) moves forward toward Adebayo (MIA) and marginal contact occurs with Adebayo's right side and arm prior to the hand-off.
Anunoby (TOR) goes to and through Tucker's (MIA) space during the screen and dislodges him.
Tucker (MIA) firms up in his screening position in Anunoby's (TOR) path and absorbs the contact.
Barnes (TOR) has his forearm rested on Butler's (MIA) left side and does not apply any force as Butler fades away during his upward shooting motion.
VanVleet (TOR) engages with Butler (MIA) off-ball and marginal contact occurs as they move into the lane.
VanVleet (TOR) and Adebayo (MIA) make incidental foot-to-foot contact with one another off-ball.
Herro (MIA) brings his off-arm toward Anunoby's (TOR) left side and marginal contact occurs as Herro turns toward the basket.
Butler (MIA) and Boucher (TOR) come together at the same spot in the lane and marginal body contact occurs as the shot is attempted.
Anunoby (TOR) and Barnes (TOR) each jump alongside Herro's (MIA) path and legally contest his jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Siakam (TOR) before any incidental contact occurs during rebounding.
Anunoby (TOR) extends for the ball and cleanly bats it toward his teammate before incidental body/arm contact occurs with Herro (MIA) during rebounding.
Vincent (MIA) commits a take foul on Barnes (TOR).

Vincent (MIA) initiates leg and arm contact with Anunoby (TOR) as Anunoby dribbles toward the block, affecting Anunoby's SQBR and causing him to travel. Anunoby's head then lands out of bounds as he falls to the floor thereafter.
Adebayo (MIA) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Vincent (MIA) makes clean contact with the ball and ties Anunoby (TOR) up as simultaneous incidental arm contact occurs. A jump ball is correctly assessed.
Barnes (TOR) and Butler (MIA) engage and disengage with one another as they each pursue the loose ball.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Barnes' (TOR) left foot lands out of bounds as he retrieves the loose ball.
VanVleet (TOR) and Vincent (MIA) engage and disengage with one another as Vincent moves to set the pick.
Butler (MIA) brings his hands forward toward Siakam's (TOR) front and marginal contact occurs as Siakam leaves his feet to pass.
Anunoby (TOR) commits a take foul on Adebayo (MIA).
